objects.description:
Snippet template shall include:

.. code-block:: rst

   .. item:: ${1:Title}
      :id: ${2:auto-id}
      :type: ${3|type1,type2,...|}
      :level: ${4|level1,level2,...|}
      :status: ${5|status1,status2,...|}
      ${6::links: }

      ${0:Description}

The extension shall support a ``customFields`` configuration
in precept.json that maps field names to lists of valid values. Each value
entry shall have:

- value: The string value used in RST (e.g., "widget-pro")
- title: Display name for documentation (e.g., "Widget Pro")

Example::

   "customFields": {
       "product": [
           {"value": "widget-pro", "title": "Widget Pro"},
           {"value": "widget-lite", "title": "Widget Lite"}
       ],
       "priority": [
           {"value": "high", "title": "High"},
           {"value": "medium", "title": "Medium"},
           {"value": "low", "title": "Low"}
       ]
   }

Diagnostic severity SHALL be configurable per error type:

.. code-block:: json

   {
     "precept.validation.errors": {
       "brokenLinks": "error",
       "duplicateIds": "error",
       "circularDeps": "warning",
       "orphanedReqs": "info",
       "statusInconsistent": "warning"
     }
   }
